Thank you Jesus for the grace that you have given me i can never repay back from my heart, i love to say that i thank you. Who am i you love me so gently, who am i? you recognise my name, who am i? you speak to me so softly a conversation with the lord most hight who am i? Amazing grace how sweet that sound you save a wretch like me i was once lost but now am found was blind but now i see. The more i sing the sweet old song, the more i understand that i do not comprehend this love you light in me adore.

Thank you Jesus for the grace that you have given me i can never repay back from my heart i love to say that i thank you.
